## Environment Description
The environment consists of a kitchen and a dining room. The kitchen has dark grey cabinets with blue handles, a light-colored marble countertop, and a sink on the left side. Above the counter, there are more dark grey cabinets. A white refrigerator is located on the right side of the kitchen, adjacent to the dining room. The dining room has a wooden table with white chairs and a light fixture on the ceiling. The floor in both rooms is made of dark wood parquet.
